{"tid":933355,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年見母被性侵捨身救　慘遭兇手打凹頭骨癱瘓逝世","createTime":"2018-12-08T13:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T06:46:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c87a11e3d9961395568df5c5357754b4a05e69c5","tid":933355,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一名16歲少年克拉皮文(Vanya Krapivin)，在去年年初放學回家時，看到43歲鄰居普羅寧(Roman Pronin)正企圖性侵她的母親娜塔莉亞(Natalia)，克拉皮文馬上衝上去與普羅寧博鬥，但反倒被普羅寧打成重傷，頭骨更大片凹陷，慘不忍睹。皮拉克文與病魔搏鬥了19個月，仍在本月4日傳來噩耗，不幸離世。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，事發當天普羅寧闖進娜塔莉亞的家，並霸王硬上弓，企圖性侵她。剛好這時克拉皮文回家，卻看到媽媽渾身是血、被普羅寧壓在地上。克拉皮文為了救母，拿起一個3公斤重的啞鈴與普羅寧決鬥，但他鬥不過普羅寧，隨後啞鈴反被普羅寧搶去，更直接狠打克拉皮文的頭部。之後克拉皮文被送醫，醫師發現克拉皮文的頭骨已經被打凹了絕大部分，並陷入昏迷9個月，可見兇手下手之兇殘，而母親娜塔莉亞也身中27刀，但保住了一命。<br />\n之後克拉皮文從美少年，變成了重殘癱瘓，讓母親相當不捨，甚至不敢常到醫院探望兒子。就在今年6月，克拉皮文的狀況一度好轉，開始能認得醫護人員，也能吃粥等軟質食物，今年7月，他住進莫斯科的一家復健中心，大家都看好他的病情能往好的方向發展。但就在10月，克拉皮文感染了流感，也讓他的病情惡化，急轉直下，更在本月4日傳來噩耗。<br />\n據悉母親娜塔莉亞至今仍無法接受及應對兒子的悲劇，她非常自責，但不發一語。而兇手普羅寧，先前因蓄意謀殺罪而被判14年徒刑，現在因為克拉皮文之死，他將再被控另一個謀殺罪。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_67cfe0a91640f55ec51d8de403947e5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_67cfe0a91640f55ec51d8de403947e5f.jpg&h=4c0f4b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_2a5fa54f56e421bc2024d6c1574033b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_2a5fa54f56e421bc2024d6c1574033b6.jpg&h=705d65c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_e4ef3ae77f02b5605009cfbccd5d7fd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_e4ef3ae77f02b5605009cfbccd5d7fd8.jpg&h=ea1e225f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_c26f58dc5a222e98a7e24870cc419b7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_c26f58dc5a222e98a7e24870cc419b7a.jpg&h=c03d26b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_b19e8b6db1f7599f58e74108ce221d3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_b19e8b6db1f7599f58e74108ce221d3e.jpg&h=fa4f855a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181208/640_3a07fa75cd67b2b1784b1abdcfd1e1ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181208%2F640_3a07fa75cd67b2b1784b1abdcfd1e1ec.jpg&h=8df9fc43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181208/1480179/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181208%2F1480179%2F&d=fSAxC%2FTA6Egen0OSdT0%2B6OI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=f62c043c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181208%2F1480179%2F&h=16e8b993\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181208/1480179/</a>"},{"pid":"104f9f87eb5ae2ad3dbf2646c94606a1d70fa41c","tid":933355,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4af42fdf8265c71fee40a9548e87bc698da6d1eb","tid":933355,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"678d3878ea2bd7f59d2e1fb8d041ce1724572ac6","tid":933355,"uid":175888,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"連燈仔: 勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"7c6d3c42e287d3ee42dd08d0661dbf9154ff475e","tid":933355,"uid":164932,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T13: